contentrichtext.text: Article [[Zhi Quan Zhou]] listed on [[Wikipedia:Votes for deletion]] Apr 20 to Apr 26 2004, consensus was to move to user namespace and delete. Discussion: * Self-created personal page, no content, not significant enough... --[[User:Robert Merkel|Robert Merkel]] 08:43, 20 Apr 2004 (UTC) * It got moved to [[User:Zhi Quan Zhou]], which ''isn't'' the user's account. It needs to be moved to [[User:Zqzhou]], and the redirects deleted. -- [[User:Cyrius|Cyrius]]|[[User talk:Cyrius|&#9998]] 10:14, Apr 20, 2004 (UTC) * I've moved it. Any reason to not just zap away the errent redirects? - [[User:UtherSRG|UtherSRG]] 00:17, 21 Apr 2004 (UTC) ** No reason not to that I see. -- [[User:Cyrius|Cyrius]]|[[User talk:Cyrius|&#9998]] 01:25, Apr 21, 2004 (UTC) ** Nope. Delete. [[User:Cribcage|Cribcage]] 05:47, 24 Apr 2004 (UTC) ''End discussion''
